{"id":"913","name":"coffee-cupcakes-update","title":"Coffee &amp; Cupcakes Update","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2008-09-04T16:54:00-05:00","tags":["coffee","cool springs galleria","crema","cupcakes","drinkhaus","espresso","gigi&apos;s cupcakes","gourmet","pumpkin spice latte","starbucks"],"categories":["Food &amp; Drink"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm1.static.flickr.com/119/297502424_47a0fdad71.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p>Some of our local coffee and cupcake makers have been very busy. Here are some of the latest updates from <a href=\"http://crema-coffee.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;crema-coffee.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Crema</a>, <a href=\"http://drinkhaus.blogspot.com/2008/09/little-buzz.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;drinkhaus.blogspot.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">DrinkHaus</a>, <a href=\"http://thesugarbar.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;thesugarbar.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Sugar Bar</a> and <a href=\"http://gigiscupcakes.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;gigiscupcakes.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Gigi&#x2019;s Cupcakes</a>:&#xA0;</p><ul><li><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CREMA </strong>is offering some great <a href=\"http://nashvillefoodies.blogspot.com/2008/09/coffee-classes-at-crema.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillefoodies.blogspot.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">coffee classes</a> this fall. Choose from <em style=\"font-style: italic;\">Espresso 101</em> (9/27; 3:30pm), <em style=\"font-style: italic;\">Brewing Techniques</em> (10/25; 3:30pm) and <em style=\"font-style: italic;\">Coffee Tasting</em> (11/15; 3:30pm). Space is very limited, so email <a href=\"mailto:rachel@crema-coffee.com\" target=\"_blank\">rachel@crema-coffee.com</a> to sign up now.&#xA0;</li><li><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DRINKHAUS</strong>&#xA0;is expanding their hours due to popular request. Starting September 15, they will be open Monday-Friday from 6am-9pm, Saturday from 9am-10pm and Sunday from 9am-3pm.&#xA0;</li><li><strong>THE SUGAR BAR</strong> is no longer setting up shop at the Farmer&#x2019;s Market every weekend. We&#x2019;re really sad, but we understand. <a href=\"http://uglymugsnashville.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;uglymugsnashville.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Ugly Mugs</a> carries their cupcakes, so we&#x2019;ll manage.&#xA0;</li><li><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GIGI&#x2019;S</strong> has set up shop in the Cool Springs Galleria. Their new cupcake stand can be found on the 2nd level near Footlocker. They&#x2019;ve conquered downtown and Cool Springs&#x2026; Next up: world domination.&#xA0;</li><li><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Pssst: </strong>Starbucks&#xA0;brought back the pumpkin spice latte yesterday morning. We <em style=\"font-style: italic;\">promise</em> that we recognize the superiority of local coffee and our local coffee shops, so take it easy on us (everyone has a guilty pleasure).&#xA0;</li></ul><div><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">Photo by </em><a href=\"http://flickr.com/photos/cafemama/297502424/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">cafemama</em></a><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">.&#xA0;</em></div><p>&#xA0;</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/01/crema-coffee-classes-guest-posts/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Crema Coffee Classes [Guest Posts]\">Crema Coffee Classes [Guest Posts]</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/19/cupcake-showdown-gigis-cupcakes-vs-dulce-desserts/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Cupcake Showdown: Gigi&#x2019;s Cupcakes vs. Dulce Desserts\">Cupcake Showdown: Gigi&#x2019;s Cupcakes vs. Dulce Desserts</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/23/cremas-got-the-coffee-spirit/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Crema&#x2019;s Got The Coffee Spirit\">Crema&#x2019;s Got The Coffee Spirit</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/03/02/you-tell-us-coffee-shops-different-strokes-for-different-folks/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: You Tell Us: Coffee Shops [Different Strokes For Different Folks]\">You Tell Us: Coffee Shops [Different Strokes For Different Folks]</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/11/20/coffee-for-christmas-please-tis-the-season/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Coffee For Christmas, Please [\" tis=\"\" the=\"\" season]'=\"\">Coffee For Christmas, Please [&apos;Tis The Season]</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}